Automated File Organizer

A Python program that organizes files into folders based on their file extensions.

Features

- Scans source directory
- Creates folders automatically
- Handles duplicate filenames
- Logs file movements
- Supports dry-run mode

 How to Run

1. Run the program:
    project one.py
2. Enter source folder path
3. Enter destination folder path

Output Example

Destination/
   Documents/
   Images/
   Audio/
   Videos/
   Other/
